thread.title: M Davis

author: M Davis
title: M Davis
text: I thought I would have to replace the old lock on my refinished desk but was able to order replacement keys from EasyKeys by using a code I found on the lock. I was so happy when the keys fit perfectly and arrived very quickly even though I didn't select expedited shipping. Now I don't have to change to a new lock that wouldn't match the age and patina of the rest of the desk hardware.
